366
00:19:19,769 --> 00:19:23,369
Bahwa ada pencuri pakaian dalam yang memegang pisau di tempat ini.

367
00:19:23,369 --> 00:19:24,769
Dia memegang pisau?

368
00:19:24,769 --> 00:19:26,069
Apa?

369
00:19:26,069 --> 00:19:27,169
